definitions.definition: ( anatomy , plural mammae ) The milk-secreting organ of female humans and other mammals which includes the mammary gland and the nipple or teat ; a breast ; an udder .
( meteorology ) An accessory cloud like a mammary in appearance, which can form on the underside of most cloud genera .
